com.microsoft.azure.storage.table

Annotation Type Ignore


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
@Documented
public @interface Ignore
    An annotation set on a method to prevent its use in serializing or deserializing a property by reflection. Apply the @Ignore annotation to methods in a class implementing TableEntity to force them to be ignored during reflection-based serialization and deserialization. See the documentation for TableServiceEntity for more information on using reflection-based serialization and deserialization.
